Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:06.57,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H5&}{\c&H372D28&\an8\move(220,55,220,-389)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\fs50\bord0}中\N学\N夏\N季\N围\N棋\N大\N赛\N会\N场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.93,0:17:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}怎么办啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}好激动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}下得不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}好紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.96,0:17:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}好可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}会变成什么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}嘿嘿 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  三谷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 还以为你不会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为你怕了海王不敢来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么傻话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个黑子 逃掉了也没什么好下场哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果逃走的话 另一片黑子就会被吃掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…吵死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筒井学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷 为什么你这么强还要作弊啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 找到了 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小明?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不用来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你看也看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近筒井学长教了我一些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提子或是数目什么的我都懂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 难得人家做了便当送过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小明好伟大!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.49,0:18:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤崎 我带你去物品存放处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷 我们来下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去真的没问题吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是叶濑中学的进藤吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶濑的?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.14,0:18:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他上次大赛赢了海王哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:18:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他那时才小学六年级
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扮成中学生来参加比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.46,0:19:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是当时他精湛的棋艺让周围的人惊叹不已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.37,0:19:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好苦恼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要尽全力就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.21,0:19:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力全力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要打败第一回合的三将…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的觉得这么简单吗? 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方也会全力以赴的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真啰嗦 我的目标可是海王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以在第一回合就输掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再全力把第二回合的海王击败的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.98,0:19:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定就能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海王的三将也会尽全力的 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待跟海王的比赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.07,0:19:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海王的三将会是什么样的人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.66,0:19:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:20:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海王的三将是我 进藤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…你会…?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.05,0:20:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记不记得你说过不会再跟我下棋了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你还说要参加围棋大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于让我等到今天了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了追赶佐为…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【GoGo】
