Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.55,0:22:28.31,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就走这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.10,0:22:32.66,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再下这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.71,0:22:34.46,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再想一想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.63,0:22:37.31,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但答案的确是这三个地方的其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:42.37,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:44.88,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H000000&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord2}{\pos(330,383)}{\fs25}{\fad(484,300)}虽然被提掉一子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:46.25,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.25,0:22:48.49,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.49,0:22:49.70,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把白子提走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.43,0:22:52.53,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优希很厉害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.39,0:22:52.39,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord3\pos(306,359)}{\1c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&HFF0000&}{\fad(0,434)}干得好                       优希!!
